\" /></a><div>Marla by suta-kaykar</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Three_Sisters\" title=\"Lord of the Three Sisters\">Lady of the Three Sisters</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Kings_on_the_Three_Sisters\" title=\"Kings on the Three Sisters\">Queen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Sunderland\" title=\"House Sunderland\">House Sunderland</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Silent_sisters\" title=\"Silent sisters\">Silent sisters</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Sistermen\" title=\"Sistermen\">Sistermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table> \n<p><b>Marla Sunderland</b> was a noblewoman of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Sunderland\" title=\"House Sunderland\">House Sunderland</a> who briefly ruled the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">Three Sisters</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Kings_on_the_Three_Sisters\" title=\"Kings on the Three Sisters\">queen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marla_Sunderland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>At the start of <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>, the lords of the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">Three Sisters</a> took advantage of the chaos in <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> and rebelled against young King <a href=\"/index.php/Ronnel_Arryn\" title=\"Ronnel Arryn\">Ronnel Arryn</a>, installing Lady Marla as their queen and launching the <a href=\"/index.php/Sistermen%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Sistermen&#39;s Rebellion\">Sistermen's Rebellion</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons_-_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons_-_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> As their fleet had largely been <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_in_the_waters_off_Gulltown\" title=\"Battle in the waters off Gulltown\">destroyed</a> during the Conquest, the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">Arryns</a> had little means of quelling the rebellion themselves.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>With the Conquest over and the Vale now part of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a>, King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a> tasked Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Torrhen_Stark\" title=\"Torrhen Stark\">Torrhen Stark</a>, newly named by the Conqueror as <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_North\" title=\"Warden of the North\">Warden of the North</a>, with suppressing the Sistermen's Rebellion. Led by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Warrick_Manderly\" title=\"Warrick Manderly\">Warrick Manderly</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">northern</a> host sailed to the Three Sisters aboard galleys hired from <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>. The sight of the sails, and the sudden appearance of Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Visenya Targaryen</a> mounted on her <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Vhagar\" title=\"Vhagar\">Vhagar</a>, took the heart out of the Sistermen. Queen Marla was deposed by her own people with her younger brother <a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Sunderland\" title=\"Steffon Sunderland\">Steffon</a> bending the knee and renewing fealty to House Arryn.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The deposed Marla was exiled and imprisoned. After five years, in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_6_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">6&#160;AC</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtrotd3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtrotd3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> she had her tongue removed and ended her days with the <a href=\"/index.php/Silent_sisters\" title=\"Silent sisters\">silent sisters</a>, tending to the noble dead.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marla_Sunderland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</sp